  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：PaCoRe</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.425\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"494\" data-imgfileid=\"100017235\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=14dccfb1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzte4ibre4WNQpVaBSwCZJXx7EMZRibrvL5r5oiazGibXKRXGOD7EkAjxmxiblUPwgE30Qp3vFKbHx8TibA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★PaCoRe通过将推理的驱动从顺序深度转向协调的并行广度，突破模型上下文限制，大规模扩展测试时间计算。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">其框架通过大规模、基于结果的强化学习训练，掌握了协调多种并行见解所需的推理合成能力。PaCoRe在多个领域表现出显著的改进，尤其是在数学领域超越了前沿系统。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/pacore\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/pacore</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：extrapolation_midtrain</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4101851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" data-height=\"478\" data-imgfileid=\"100017234\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eb50bda4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzte4ibre4WNQpVaBSwCZJXx2xDssVyI4Z0GHScI3bWTURO7EzbD3z4c3icOYzma93y9ZUYoC6Y0Fng%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★extrapolation_midtrain项目探讨了强化学习在扩展语言模型推理能力方面的有效性。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">研究通过构建一个完全受控的实验框架，分析预训练、中期训练和基于RL的后训练如何共同塑造语言模型的推理能力。使用合成的数学风格推理任务，研究了模型在更复杂组合和多样化语境中的泛化能力，以及RL如何与先验知识交互并在何时超越预训练带来真正的能力提升。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/extrapolation-midtrain\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/extrapolation-midtrain</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Dual-Flow</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.41574074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" data-height=\"484\" data-imgfileid=\"100017232\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=40fd52e7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzte4ibre4WNQpVaBSwCZJXxLE6yYnAPqk7lSp3FTibdx514tauJwIQ2uRQrsb3qVxjibTII7NiawvlXw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Dual-Flow项目旨在通过野外级联流优化实现可迁移的多目标、实例无关攻击。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目提出了一种新颖的方法，能够在不依赖特定实例的情况下，对多个目标进行攻击。通过使用Res152和Incv3作为Agent模型，项目提供了多种权重配置，以适应不同的任务需求。项目的创新在于其优化流程和多目标攻击的能力，适用于图像分类等任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/dual-flow\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/dual-flow</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Authentic-Dubber</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.43796296296296294\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" data-height=\"510\" data-imgfileid=\"100017233\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=04ea718f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzte4ibre4WNQpVaBSwCZJXxzJa8zBOjOgmS4ibPrGG1oG5ISLMKGHwVibUf7Hx7qBQMtr2ANCzCicerQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Authentic-Dubber 是一个自动电影配音模型，旨在通过检索增强的导演-演员互动学习实现真实的电影配音。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">构建多模态参考素材库</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">、</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">情感相似性检索增强策略</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">以及</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">进阶图语音生成方法</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，模拟真实的配音工作流程，提升情感表达的全面性。项目在 V2C 动画基准数据集上的主观和客观评估验证了其有效性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/authentic-dubber\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/authentic-dubber</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：4DSloMo</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.31574074074074077\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1160\" data-height=\"366\" data-imgfileid=\"100017236\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d56647ae&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzte4ibre4WNQpVaBSwCZJXx0ECwpDicxKhINocQ9zVjCLVQoYK3mkmph5enWxiasbRNpDDCa9wAzhPA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★4DSloMo项目旨在实现对高速场景的4D重建，采用异步捕获技术。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目利用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">深度学习</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">图像处理</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">技术，能够在不同时刻捕获的图像中重建出高质量的4D场景。项目的目标是为计算机视觉领域提供一种新的解决方案，特别是在需要高精度和高速度的场景重建任务中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/4dslomo\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/4dslomo</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：CoIDO</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6287037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" data-height=\"732\" data-imgfileid=\"100017237\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=396afd49&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzte4ibre4WNQpVaBSwCZJXxl3kzpnvjY7944vxP92lEa8S0UR8LL2RgWqekL4w85zl0JRxRgZovCg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★CoIDO项目旨在通过耦合重要性-多样性优化实现高效的数据选择，以提升视觉指令调优的效果。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目提供了一套完整的数据处理和训练管道，利用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">多模态特征</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">进行数据难度预测，并通过数据选择策略确保数据集的多样性和高质量。项目中使用了多种预训练模型和特征提取方法，支持多种数据处理和聚类技术。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/coido\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/coido</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文汇总并介绍了六款最新的开源 AI 项目，涵盖大模型推理框架、强化学习模型、多目标攻击框架、自动配音模型、高速场景 4D 重建以及视觉指令调优数据选择工具。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文汇总并介绍了六款最新的开源 AI 项目，涵盖大模型推理框架、强化学习模型、多目标攻击框架、自动配音模型、高速场景 4D 重建以及视觉指令调优数据选择工具。",
  "summary": "文章以“今日开源”的形式，快速浏览了 6 个近期发布的 AI 领域开源项目。首先介绍了阶跃星辰的 PaCoRe 框架，该框架通过并行广度推理突破大模型上下文限制，实现百万 Token 处理。随后，extrapolation_midtrain 项目探讨了强化学习如何增强语言模型推理能力。在工具框架方面，Dual-Flow 提出可迁移多目标攻击方法；Authentic-Dubber 是利用检索增强进行真实电影自动配音的模型；4DSloMo 专注于高速场景的 4D 重建。最后，CoIDO 项目通过耦合重要性-多样性优化实现高效数据选择，提升视觉指令调优效果。整体而言，文章对这些前沿 AI 项目进行了简要概述，每个项目都附有简介和一键收藏链接。该文章更偏向于 AI 技术领域的资讯汇总，而非深入的技术报告。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "PaCoRe 框架通过并行广度推理突破大模型上下文限制，提升推理效率。",
      "explanation": "该框架将推理驱动从顺序深度转变为协调的并行广度，大规模扩展测试时间计算，尤其在数学领域表现突出，实现了百万 Token 并行推理，体现了 AI 模型在效率和规模上的突破。"
    },
